"me,\""],[32,"says"],[33,"Akka."]]},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32392/size6/8ca2b9a13fe714dff6fd3e26c3c2140f.jpg","text":"\"Don’t\nyou dare break anything!\" says Thaatha.  \n\"You're\ndisturbing the class,\" says his teacher.","words":[[34,"\"Don’t"],[35,"you"],[36,"dare"],[37,"break"],[38,"anything!\""],[39,"says"],[40,"Thaatha."],[41,"\"You're"],[42,"disturbing"],[43,"the"],[44,"class,\""],[45,"says"],[46,"his"],[47,"teacher."]]},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32428/size6/23081b831abf10ecb4afcce065f3b1e1.jpg","text":"But\nwhat can Satya do \nif his hands and legs are always dancing?","words":[[48,"But"],[49,"what"],[50,"can"],[51,"Satya"],[52,"do"],[53,"if"],[54,"his"],[55,"hands"],[56,"and"],[57,"legs"],[58,"are"],[59,"always"],[60,"dancing?"]]},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32394/size6/d7bd0406ad67082d13ab3f07a53ac51d.jpg","text":"Today is Sunday.\nIt’s Satya’s favourite day of the week — the day he goes to the farm where Amma works.","words":[[61,"Today"],[62,"is"],[63,"Sunday."],[64,"It’s"],[65,"Satya’s"],[66,"favourite"],[67,"day"],[68,"of"],[69,"the"],[70,"week"],[71,"—"],[72,"the"],[73,"day"],[74,"he"],[75,"goes"],[76,"to"],[77,"the"],[78,"farm"],[79,"where"],[80,"Amma"],[81,"works."]]},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32395/size6/aa5bce1d50536b52f4a2f2b6e3e9c940.jpg","text":"It’s a long walk to the farm, through secret up-and-down paths, open fields, thick forests and gently flowing streams.","words":[[82,"It’s"],[83,"a"],[84,"long"],[85,"walk"],[86,"to"],[87,"the"],[88,"farm,"],[89,"through"],[90,"secret"],[91,"up-and-down"],[92,"paths,"],[93,"open"],[94,"fields,"],[95,"thick"],[96,"forests"],[97,"and"],[98,"gently"],[99,"flowing"],[100,"streams."]]},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32396/size6/d523bd41a658f087d7b0c52c9d60a847.jpg","text":"Satya hops like a hare and sprints like a deer.  \n\"The mud is squishy. Be careful!\" says Amma.","words":[[101,"Satya"],[102,"hops"],[103,"like"],[104,"a"],[105,"hare"],[106,"and"],[107,"sprints"],[108,"like"],[109,"a"],[110,"deer."],[111,"\"The"],[112,"mud"],[113,"is"],[114,"squishy."],[115,"Be"],[116,"careful!\""],[117,"says"],[118,"Amma."]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32397/size6/f9a9f04bd680812c6340c684372c9ffc.jpg","text":"He crawls like a centipede and slithers like a snake.\n\"Look out for thorns!\" says Amma.","words":[[119,"He"],[120,"crawls"],[121,"like"],[122,"a"],[123,"centipede"],[124,"and"],[125,"slithers"],[126,"like"],[127,"a"],[128,"snake."],[129,"\"Look"],[130,"out"],[131,"for"],[132,"thorns!\""],[133,"says"],[134,"Amma."]]},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32401/size6/1c15bfd50d1de6371f39a67878bf021a.jpg","text":"He swings like a spider and leaps like a langur.\n\"Wheeeee!\"\n\"Use the strong branches, my little monkey,\" says Amma.","words":[[135,"He"],[136,"swings"],[137,"like"],[138,"a"],[139,"spider"],[140,"and"],[141,"leaps"],[142,"like"],[143,"a"],[144,"langur."],[145,"\"Wheeeee!\""],[146,"\"Use"],[147,"the"],[148,"strong"],[149,"branches,"],[150,"my"],[151,"little"],[152,"monkey,\""],[153,"says"],[154,"Amma."]]},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32405/size6/a39f86362a213873464a8f73120dbea1.jpg","text":"He paddles like a duck and  swims like a frog.\n\"Stay in the shallows, okay?\" says Amma.","words":[[155,"He"],[156,"paddles"],[157,"like"],[158,"a"],[159,"duck"],[160,"and"],[161,"swims"],[162,"like"],[163,"a"],[164,"frog."],[165,"\"Stay"],[166,"in"],[167,"the"],[168,"shallows,"],[169,"okay?\""],[170,"says"],[171,"Amma."]]},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32408/size6/fb9a5fc9ee10684eb6c1bb68827944f9.jpg","text":"He climbs like a lizard and jumps like a goat.\n\"Don’t slip!\" says Amma.","words":[[172,"He"],[173,"climbs"],[174,"like"],[175,"a"],[176,"lizard"],[177,"and"],[178,"jumps"],[179,"like"],[180,"a"],[181,"goat."],[182,"\"Don’t"],[183,"slip!\""],[184,"says"],[185,"Amma."]]},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32422/size6/86aab2a2afe0135ae9442b74383ea190.jpg","text":"Satya flaps his arms like wings and tries to fly away. \nHe imagines himself soaring and gliding like a vulture.","words":[[186,"Satya"],[187,"flaps"],[188,"his"],[189,"arms"],[190,"like"],[191,"wings"],[192,"and"],[193,"tries"],[194,"to"],[195,"fly"],[196,"away."],[197,"He"],[198,"imagines"],[199,"himself"],[200,"soaring"],[201,"and"],[202,"gliding"],[203,"like"],[204,"a"],[205,"vulture."]]},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32410/size6/363e8ed0bd2a4148902cdda7789ac4a4.jpg","text":"Late in the evening, when the sun sets and crickets begin to hum, it’s time to go home.\nTired Satya climbs on to his mother's back. They return through the up-and-down paths, fields, forests and streams.","words":[[206,"Late"],[207,"in"],[208,"the"],[209,"evening,"],[210,"when"],[211,"the"],[212,"sun"],[213,"sets"],[214,"and"],[215,"crickets"],[216,"begin"],[217,"to"],[218,"hum,"],[219,"it’s"],[220,"time"],[221,"to"],[222,"go"],[223,"home."],[224,"Tired"],[225,"Satya"],[226,"climbs"],[227,"on"],[228,"to"],[229,"his"],[230,"mother's"],[231,"back."],[232,"They"],[233,"return"],[234,"through"],[235,"the"],[236,"up-and-down"],[237,"paths,"],[238,"fields,"],[239,"forests"],[240,"and"],[241,"streams."]]},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32411/size6/a957a52179a5a361e2d8efbd9fa7b028.jpg","text":"At\nhome, Appa, Akka and Thaatha take one look at bruised and muddy\nSatya, and burst into laughter.","words":[[242,"At"],[243,"home,"],[244,"Appa,"],[245,"Akka"],[246,"and"],[247,"Thaatha"],[248,"take"],[249,"one"],[250,"look"],[251,"at"],[252,"bruised"],[253,"and"],[254,"muddy"],[255,"Satya,"],[256,"and"],[257,"burst"],[258,"into"],[259,"laughter."]]},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32429/size6/a638fe5e531fdeadd9662e6c03fa9994.jpg","text":"Thaatha bathes him.\nAppa cooks him dinner.\nAkka tells him his favourite story as he falls asleep.","words":[[260,"Thaatha"],[261,"bathes"],[262,"him."],[263,"Appa"],[264,"cooks"],[265,"him"],[266,"dinner."],[267,"Akka"],[268,"tells"],[269,"him"],[270,"his"],[271,"favourite"],[272,"story"],[273,"as"],[274,"he"],[275,"falls"],[276,"asleep."]]},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32413/size6/55101aafad0ca19fa44f9754a321fce4.jpg","text":"In\nhis dreams, Satya runs and jumps and spins and rolls...","words":[[277,"In"],[278,"his"],[279,"dreams,"],[280,"Satya"],[281,"runs"],[282,"and"],[283,"jumps"],[284,"and"],[285,"spins"],[286,"and"],[287,"rolls..."]]},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32414/size6/80f9718b7aa40d81a56ac34b97093339.jpg","text":"... and\nflies away!","words":[[288,"..."],[289,"and"],[290,"flies"],[291,"away!"]]},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/32549/size6/974e365c0030bbfa203ccebbe77a38e4.jpg","text":"How\ndo they move?\nOh, the way Satya moves! Did you know that animals, birds and insects also move in many different ways and for different reasons?\nLike us, they move mainly to find\ndelicious food, a cozy home and a warm family. Some of them also move\nto escape from being caught and eaten by other animals.\nFind out how some of these\ncreatures move!","words":[[292,"How"],[293,"do"],[294,"they"],[295,"move?"],[296,"Oh,"],[297,"the"],[298,"way"],[299,"Satya"],[300,"moves!"],[301,"D